description: Abide by the Rules of Acquisition and untold wealth may be yours.  You may ask for specific rules or request a random rule.  Non-canon rules are included, for a total of 285 profit-maximizing proverbs.  And remember, "When no appropriate rule applies... make one up."
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask rules of acquisition for a rule.

shortDescription: Behold the Rules of Acquisition!  May profit forever be your guiding principle.
